<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <p xml:id="Aink226-kilavi">varaiviṭai vaittup pirinta talaimakaṉ nīṭṭittu vantuḻit tōḻi talaimakaṭkuc colliyatu. </p>
      <p xml:lang="en">What the confidante told the heroine, when the hero—who had separated after placing an interval [before the time of] marriage—had come, having delayed.</p>
    </div>
  <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink226">
<l>amma vāḻi tōḻi nammalai</l>
<l>naṟuntaṇ cilampi ṉāṟukulaik kāntaṭ</l>
<l>koṅkuṇ vaṇṭiṟ peyarntu puṟamāṟiniṉ</l>
<l>vaṉpuṭai viṟaṟkaviṉ koṇṭa</l>
<l>vaṉpilāḷaṉ vantaṉa ṉiṉiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l>  O friend! </l>
        <l rend="space indent">just like the bees that consume the honey of Malabar glory lilies  </l>
        <l rend="indent">[that grow] in fragrant clusters along the fragrant, cool slopes of our mountain, </l>
        <l rend="space indent2">so too the loveless man,   </l>
        <l rend="indent2">who had taken your strong, victorious beauty, </l>
        <l rend="indent2">has come now. </l>

      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
